{"tid":765018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又贏】蘋果 App Store 被指滿遍「黃賭毒」　中國官媒怒吼了","createTime":"2018-08-02T12:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T03:09:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6394ec149928c8213bfd768158b1296e207f0d27","tid":765018,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"中央電視台第 13 套新聞頻道以「蘋果官方應用商店管理存漏洞」為標題進行長達 34 分鐘的綜合報導，批評蘋果監管應用程式上架不力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外新華社更以「黃、賭、藥都敢發！蘋果，你怎麼連這樣的事都不管？」為題批評蘋果的審核政策，並踢爆利用 iMessage 作賭場、色情、貸款等垃圾內容的產業鏈，發送 iMessage 垃圾訊息每條付人民幣 7 分，50000 條以上甚至可以議價。這些垃圾短訊需要用戶的 Apple ID 電郵才能傳送，甚至令用戶的訊息洩漏出去，有中國的律師按示蘋果在技術上無法完全阻止有關垃圾訊息傳送，要對垃圾訊息承擔一定責任。<br />\n<br />\n新華社指中國工信部會牽頭 13 個部門從 2018 年 7 月開始的 1 年半時間之內採取行動，全面打擊有關垃圾短訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/08/02/app-store-imessage-is-polluted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2Fapp-store-imessage-is-polluted%2F&d=0%2Fn9LnBUZpXCn3HzwSPaeqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8970b8d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/08/02/app-store-imessage-is-polluted/</a>"},{"pid":"56b9a827f8140058b6b6aa2f15d55528863803b6","tid":765018,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"apple 死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966d0e211d0e7acc2b441b1f841fbd70311449be","tid":765018,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"禁用iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae373c13709756706f135f2e7fabeebbdbb44dd4","tid":765018,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"Die soon <br />\nDrop to zero"},{"pid":"1db8510fc0a01f74a5454f0f2a1aad6227c08dce","tid":765018,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"係都幾